# Feature branch workflow

- For any new feature, do not implement directly on `main`.
- Create (or switch to) a dedicated feature branch before coding.
- Prefer branch names like `feature/<short-description>` (for example, `feature/add-doc-cache`).
- Keep commits for feature work on that branch until merged.
- If already on `main` when feature work is requested, first create a new branch and continue there.
